      div.card 
        h3 Dancing Moves
        div.card-box
          div.card-img
            img(src="/static/img/2.png")
          div.card-content
           p Every Type of DANCING MOVES you can PERFECT.

      div.card 
        h3 Dancing Exercises
        div.card-box
          div.card-img
            img(src="/static/img/3.png")
          div.card-content
           p Exercises to FLEXIBLE your body and enhance your SKILLS.

      div.card 
        h3 Hip-Hop Style
        div.card-box
          div.card-img
            img(src="/static/img/4.png")
          div.card-content
           p HIP-HOP Genre Dance Style you can PERFECT.

      div.card 
        h3 Bollywood Style
        div.card-box
          div.card-img
            img(src="/static/img/5.png")
